{"tid":1632532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［行動］行動整合Post","createTime":"2019-10-06T18:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:38:07.000Z","uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c27fb0b93f6a9c17cf1f94fb3375b6d836d1826b","tid":1632532,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:24:10.000Z","msg":"近日 連登<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">分化撚</span></span>實在太多 成個熱門7成係鬧交分化post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行動POST呢？？</span><br />\n<br />\n所以小弟想開個post整合行動嘅文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n麻煩大家推推佢 比大家見到行動風向<br />\n<br />\n如有遺漏請幫小弟後補<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9r8gLa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9r8gLa.jpg&h=0d27a920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K7kUciw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK7kUciw.jpg&h=1d993ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有巴打建議10月10 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">黃店爆買日</span></span><br />\n我認為可行 更可以配合18區開花<br />\n所以借此推推佢<br />\n十月十號 黃店爆買日 試行！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1632001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1632001</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qFOCaaP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqFOCaaP.png&h=6f6dfe83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外想喺度推埋一啲行動守則 例如<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">裝修、神獸</span></strong></span><br />\n小弟認為此post守則合理 而且正負皮數反映支持度  <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">有參考價值</span><br />\n所以亦借此推推佢<br />\n［共識］裝修、鶳了set底線<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631684</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ST99LJU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FST99LJU.jpg&h=cfbced60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\np牌仔 有錯請更請 有漏請幫補 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"4443e4aa1697d0464990cb7ba65db417133ae77f","tid":1632532,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:26:27.000Z","msg":"p牌仔推唔起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65baa99170ce1547c9a421f230168ae6eeb96804","tid":1632532,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:27:14.000Z","msg":"求下你哋幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c357b481266cae251841bd96e66157dc919b9892","tid":1632532,"uid":193520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:28:59.000Z","msg":"點都不割<br />\n但熱門d 分化post 真係睇到人心煩<br />\n好耐未試過幾個鐘都唔手痕掃熱門 今日係第一次<br />\n<br />\n愈係咁多post 就知對家有幾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d299c2ae24222eb2743dc0c43bd5a4daea4ef4","tid":1632532,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T18:29:03.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf1d2019b0eeb95f0679d4b92502a101a6e3029","tid":1632532,"uid":301632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c357b481266cae251841bd96e66157dc919b9892","tid":1632532,"uid":193520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-